SFO SKY SCOOP
SFO HELICOPTER AIRLINES, INC.. P. O. Box 2525. Oakland, CA 94614
5/71
April 25th has already passed and we didn't change our schedule.
Since many of the
carriers had major changes due in May and June. we felt it best to wait until these chances
were firm.
Our new schedule will become eftective on June I. 1971
There will be no changes in our Oakland/San Francisco service.
Two additional flights
have been added to our Berkeley and Marin County routes in response to passenger requests.
following is the new Berkeley/Marin County schedule.
You might note that there have
some minor changes on flight times to corove our connections o and rom other airlines.
